listing.name: Canal view apartment In the Center

user.about:
Hi Travelers:))

Dutch people always find it hard to describe them selfs but there you go i have to give it a try.

I am a 35 year old Single male. Oh i forgot this is not a dating site:)))

Well i once but a long time ago finished my Business studies and got a bachelors degree. I have since had many jobs varying from bartending to life guard to financial advisor to head hunter to sports sales man and now i am also renting out an apartment or few.

I enjoy doing this work very much as i am a service minded person.

I hope to make your stay in Amsterdam a pleasant one.

Kind regards,

Hev

listing.access:
For Check in after 23:00 (11 pm) you will be requested to pay 20 euro extra in cash on arrival at the apartment tot the person doing the check in.

The guests have access to the whole apartment.
listing.house_rules:
NO loud music in the apartment!
It is not allowed to sleep with more then 3 people in the apartment.
Smoking is allowed but please air the room during or after smoking.
listing.space:
The apartment is about 60 m2 and has 1 bedroom a kitchen and bathroom. All private! It can sleep in total 3 people.
The living room can sleep the third person on the sofa bed which is 110-190 cm when folded out.
The living room has: cable tv; dvd player; wifi internet; fridge/freezer; a lot of light from outside. 
The kitchen has: stove; oven/microwave; espresso machine; water kettle; sink; pots and pans; cutlery; plates and glasses. 
The Bathroom has: Shower; toilet and sink. 
The Bedroom has: 1 double bed (1 big mattress). The size is 160-200 cm / queen size bed.
listing.summary:
I offer you a spacious and nicely decorated apartment on the Beautiful Amstel Canal in Amsterdam City Center.

From this location you can walk to all the hotspots amsterdam has to offer. So no need of public transport or taxi.
listing.additional_house_rules:
NO loud music in the apartment!
It is not allowed to sleep with more then 3 people in the apartment.
Smoking is allowed but please air the room during or after smoking.

review.comments: Easy check-in and check-out. Overall great experience.
